---
import MainLayout from "../components/MainLayout.astro";
import { buildContactPageSchema } from "../utils/schema";

const canonicalPath = "/contact";
const title = "Contact";
const summary =
  "Structured enquiries for advisory, bespoke research, and operator-level automation decisions.";
const schema = [
  buildContactPageSchema({
    title,
    description:
      "Structured enquiries for advisory, bespoke research, and warehouse automation decisions.",
    canonicalPath,
  }),
];
---

<MainLayout
  canonicalPath={canonicalPath}
  title={title}
  summary={summary}
  seoTitle="Contact | Autonomy Bridge"
  seoDescription="Structured enquiries for advisory, bespoke research, and warehouse automation decisions."
  schema={schema}
>
  <article class="max-w-[1100px] mx-auto px-6 py-12 md:py-16">
    <header>
      <div class="max-w-[760px]">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-4">Contact</h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mb-8">
          Structured enquiries for advisory, bespoke research, and operator-level automation
          decisions.
        </p>
        <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800">
          Autonomy Bridge works with a focused set of clients and questions. Use this form if you
          are evaluating a warehouse automation or AI infrastructure decision, conducting investment
          or market diligence, or seeking independent research support.
        </p>
        <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800 mt-4">
          The form is designed to make scoping faster. Clear inputs lead to a faster yes, no, or
          next-step decision.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-4 gap-y-2 mt-6 text-sm">
          <a href="/advisory" class="underline underline-offset-4">Advisory &rarr;</a>
          <a href="/bespoke-research" class="underline underline-offset-4">Bespoke Research &rarr;</a>
          <a href="/frameworks" class="underline underline-offset-4">Frameworks &rarr;</a>
          <a href="/use-cases" class="underline underline-offset-4">Use Cases &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-neutral-200 md:grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-10 md:gap-12">
      <div class="md:col-span-5">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-4">What this form is for</h2>
          <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800">
            Use this form if you need support with:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 mt-4 text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800">
            <li>warehouse automation evaluation</li>
            <li>robotics deployment or vendor assessment</li>
            <li>bespoke market or buyer research</li>
            <li>investment diligence on operators, vendors, or market segments</li>
            <li>media or publisher enquiries related to industrial automation</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-neutral-200">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-4">What to include</h2>
          <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800">
            A useful enquiry usually includes:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 mt-4 text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800">
            <li>company or organization</li>
            <li>your role</li>
            <li>the decision being made</li>
            <li>the technology, market, or deployment context</li>
            <li>any timing constraint</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800 mt-4">
            The clearer the question, the faster the scoping decision.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-neutral-200">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-4">Response Time</h2>
          <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800">
            All enquiries are reviewed within two business days.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-neutral-200">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-4">Alternative Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800">
            <a
              href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/deepakgupta5"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="underline underline-offset-4"
            >
              LinkedIn
            </a>
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-7">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-4">Enquiry Form</h2>
          <form
            name="contact"
            method="POST"
            data-netlify="true"
            netlify-honeypot="bot-field"
            class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-200 bg-white p-6 md:p-8 space-y-5"
          >
            <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="contact" />
            <div aria-hidden="true" class="hidden">
              <input type="text" name="bot-field" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" />
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-2">
              <label for="name" class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900">Name</label>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">Your full name</p>
              <input
                id="name"
                name="name"
                type="text"
                required
                class="w-full rounded-md border border-neutral-300 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-base text-neutral-900 placeholder:text-neutral-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-neutral-900/10 focus:border-neutral-900"
              />
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-2">
              <label for="company" class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900">Company</label>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">Organization name</p>
              <input
                id="company"
                name="company"
                type="text"
                class="w-full rounded-md border border-neutral-300 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-base text-neutral-900 placeholder:text-neutral-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-neutral-900/10 focus:border-neutral-900"
              />
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-2">
              <label for="role" class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900">Role</label>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">Your title or function</p>
              <input
                id="role"
                name="role"
                type="text"
                class="w-full rounded-md border border-neutral-300 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-base text-neutral-900 placeholder:text-neutral-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-neutral-900/10 focus:border-neutral-900"
              />
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-2">
              <label for="enquiryType" class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900">Enquiry Type</label>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">Select the type of enquiry</p>
              <select
                id="enquiryType"
                name="enquiryType"
                required
                class="w-full rounded-md border border-neutral-300 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-base text-neutral-900 placeholder:text-neutral-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-neutral-900/10 focus:border-neutral-900"
              >
                <option value="">Select one</option>
                <option>Advisory</option>
                <option>Bespoke Research</option>
                <option>Investment / Diligence</option>
                <option>Media / Press</option>
                <option>Other</option>
              </select>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-2">
              <label for="message" class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900">Message</label>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">
                Describe the decision, context, and what you need.
              </p>
              <textarea
                id="message"
                name="message"
                required
                class="w-full rounded-md border border-neutral-300 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-base text-neutral-900 placeholder:text-neutral-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-neutral-900/10 focus:border-neutral-900 min-h-[180px] resize-y"
              ></textarea>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">
                Useful inputs include company context, your role, the decision being made, relevant
                technology or market details, and any timing constraint.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <button
                type="submit"
                class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md bg-neutral-900 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition-colors hover:bg-neutral-700"
              >
                Submit enquiry
              </button>
            </div>
          </form>
        </section>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-neutral-200">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-4">What Happens Next</h2>
      <section>
        <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold mb-2">1. Review</h3>
        <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800">
          Every enquiry is read in full before any response is sent. If the work falls outside
          current scope or capacity, the reply should say so directly.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mt-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold mb-2">2. Scoping Conversation</h3>
        <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800">
          If there is a fit, a short working call is scheduled. The purpose is to define the
          problem, not run a sales process.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mt-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold mb-2">3. Proposal or Research Brief</h3>
        <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800">
          If the engagement moves forward, the next step is a scoped proposal or a structured
          research brief covering methodology, deliverables, and timeline.
        </p>
      </section>
    </section>
  </article>
</MainLayout>
